{
  "stem": "19895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had probably one of the very best record of attendance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was an average student.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I received my matura.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I-- matura means matured from education at age 18, which in European education is a rather important moment of celebration, as well as reaching the age when you finished your gymnasium studies.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that ends that period, as far as education goes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I would say that that school, the Budapest Jewish gymnasium, was a very special institution.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one of the most beautiful school building in the city, or at least up with any other school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And its education-- and I like to talk about the school, because the school means a lot to me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That school has produced and educated a lot of good students who achieved in life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and many of them, unfortunately, didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on the other hand, those who survived have given to the world some, some fine learned and educated people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the classmates of mine, we started about 56, 57 children at age 10.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in two class-- Class B, Class B, which just a parallel class of some 54 or 58 people, the exact number.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the war ended, the two class was combined.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because unfortunately, only about 24 of the classmates did survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The rest of them perished during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- as I mentioned, I was very friendly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and I was a fairly popular young man in my class.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after World War II and after the Hungarian revolution in '56 when, when I came to the United States, which we will talk about later on in, in more detail, I have always made an effort to keep up with my classmates who all spread out all over the world.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
